lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah, uh-huh
This one's for all the dreamers out there
Listen up, let's go

[Verse 1]
I wake up every morning with a fire in my soul
Got dreams so big, they could swallow me whole
But the road ain't easy, nah, it's full of twists and turns
Gotta stay focused, gotta let my fire burn

I'm like Kanye in the game, unstoppable force
Every challenge I face, I stay on course
Through the highs and the lows, I keep my head high
With Kanye's confidence, I reach for the sky

[verse]
Kanye, the lyrical genius with a flair
Controversial and bold, he's beyond compare
Flashing lights, his creativity shines bright
Breaking boundaries, he dominates the mic

[chorus]
Kanye West, he's the king of the throne
Innovation is his style, it's all he's known
Never afraid to speak his mind, he won't rest
Kanye West, we salute you, you're the best
